    "description": "Zoho Corporation Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Full Stack Developer to join our dynamic team in Kochi. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Zoho Corporation Holdings Services:\nZoho Corporation Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zoho Corporation Holdings Services!",
